\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\underbrace{\vec{Q}_{n}\cdots\vec{Q}_{2}\vec{Q}_{1}}_{\vec{Q}^{T}}\vec{A}=\vec{R}
\]

\end_inset

and in turn we get full QR factorization 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{A}=\vec{Q}\vec{R}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

